</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Wouldn=E2=80=99t it be amazing to lear=
n that GameStop Corp.=E2=80=99s whole turnaround plan =E2=80=94=C2=A0the pl=
an that turned it from an $18.84 stock at the end of 2020 to a $325 stock a=
 month later, the plan that made it a darling of retail investors, the plan=
 that got it a bunch of <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/=
click/27125022.276601/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljb=
