e=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width:=
 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-=
color: #ccc;"> new high-powered executives</a> to execute its move into onl=
ine retail and also <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/clic=
k/27125022.276601/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwM=
