1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;"> the authorities said yes</a>. Presumably they=C2=A0figured th=
at getting Russian dollars to U.S. and European bondholders (1) was good fo=
r those bondholders and (2) wasn=E2=80=99t particularly helpful to Russia=
=E2=80=99s war effort.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But the U.S. a=
nd the European Union=C2=A0<em>do=C2=A0</em>have an interest in stopping ot=
